(5261, 130, 'add_performance_2_performance_details', 'Designed 5G NR RAN network and lead planning and deployment strategy including\r\ncost analysis, radio network, devices and test tools. Leading discussions with network,\r\nchipset and device vendors. Spearheading efforts with technical and business teams on\r\n5G and IoT use cases such as fixed wireless access, public safety etc.\r\nHeading cloud/virtual RAN solutions and technology efforts. Responsible for leading\r\nengagements on Cloud, IoT, mobility and 5G.\r\nSuccessfully tested and deployed Internet of Things (IoT – Cat-M1). Included developing\r\ndeployment strategy, device ecosystem analysis, band selection, authoring high level\r\ndesign, leading initial trials and overseeing network wide rollout.\r\n\r\nSuccessfully led the trial, deployment and testing of E-911 over VoLTE. Successfully\r\nLed\r\nthe deployment of more than 30 LTE features including Carrier Aggregation, VoLTE, and\r\nLAA resulting in significant network improvement'),
